Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.30,0:01:34.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Passing Time
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.90,0:01:54.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see, 135 over 80.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.45,0:01:59.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not bad, Someji.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.12,0:02:01.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.58,0:02:03.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I'm talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.29,0:02:05.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your blood pressure has gone down quite a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.58,0:02:08.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm going to give you more medicine.\NKeep taking it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.88,0:02:11.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sure thing. Lay it on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.54,0:02:13.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,About three months' worth.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.34,0:02:23.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}SAKUMA, MD\NInternal Medicine\NPediatrics
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.71,0:02:16.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot, I can't give you that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.01,0:02:19.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Three weeks' worth.\NCome back again next month for more.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.43,0:02:23.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Feh. All right, fine. Guess I'll see you then.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.72,0:02:27.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But you really have changed, Someji.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.94,0:02:31.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A long time ago, you were like,\N"I'm not counting on any doctor!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.61,0:02:36.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You used to say, "I'll live how I want to,\Nand die whenever!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.24,0:02:43.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Well, my wife and daughter\Nleft me with three little ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.54,0:02:47.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For them, I'm all they have.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.91,0:02:55.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come hell or high water, I have to stay alive\Nuntil all three of them are married off.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.30,0:03:05.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No way can I let them stand in front of\Nthat gold leaf folding screen alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.18,0:03:08.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Someji...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.19,0:03:11.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But still...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.69,0:03:19.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,With Momo, it'd help me out\Nif she got married as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.16,0:03:21.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}HMMM
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.95,0:03:24.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}The youngest, huh? How old is she again?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.83,0:03:26.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}SQUEEE
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.45,0:03:27.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}MUD BALLS
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.79,0:03:29.66,DefaultLow,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,PRESCHOOLER
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.87,0:03:32.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She's still in preschool.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.88,0:03:36.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If she got married just after 20, I'd be...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.84,0:03:39.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,in my mid-90s?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.72,0:03:43.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Someji.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.97,0:03:46.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't look after you for that long.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.81,0:03:56.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Five more days until the entrance exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.90,0:04:00.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so nervous!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.32,0:04:04.07,DefaultRightH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GROAN
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.61,0:04:04.07,LeftSignM,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ARGH
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.32,0:04:08.08,DefaultRightH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AOWWW
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.32,0:04:08.08,DefaultLeftH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MEOWWW
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.32,0:04:08.08,DefaultLow2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The anxiety is spreading
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.08,0:04:08.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}Got hooked in,\Nand crying as well
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.58,0:04:10.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You've done everything you could.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.66,0:04:14.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even your weakest area, proof problems,\Nyou got up to an average score of 80 or higher.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.09,0:04:16.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So you'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.38,0:04:20.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now we should just\Nreview everything thoroughly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.76,0:04:25.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And if there's anything you're still unsure of,\Nwe'll practice it again with a worksheet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.85,0:04:30.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.68,0:04:32.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Takahashi said
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.14,0:04:36.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,he's going to a private school in Kouchi, Shikoku,\Nthanks to a recommendation, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.87,0:04:47.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.12,0:04:53.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hina, you didn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.21,0:04:56.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In Shikoku?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.88,0:05:05.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When I saw her surprised face,\Nwhich looked like that of a young child,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.01,0:05:10.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}It felt like I had...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.73,0:05:14.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}broken a small egg.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.07,0:05:25.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'd heard he was going to the high school\Naffiliated with Meitei University.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.03,0:05:30.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's what he said before.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.16,0:05:33.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.63,0:05:39.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shikoku?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.00,0:05:43.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's so far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.11,0:06:03.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I thought she already knew about it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.44,0:06:06.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wish I'd never said anything.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.03,0:06:12.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}What the hell am I doing?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.12,0:06:15.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}With the exam just days away...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.16,0:06:18.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}And she worked so hard for this, too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.05,0:06:25.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}I made her feel so terrible.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.55,0:06:29.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But she only feels this way because...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.31,0:06:38.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}it's Takahashi, after all.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.69,0:06:47.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Hina, are you out grocery shopping?\NThat's wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.07,0:06:50.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, Mrs. Yamada.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.49,0:06:56.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}TSUKUDANI
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.08,0:06:57.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It hasn't changed since I was a kid.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.16,0:06:59.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My town.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.25,0:07:02.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}YAMADA STORE
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.46,0:07:02.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The scenery of the neighborhood...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.75,0:07:07.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Drink Milk to Be Healthy\NTakahashi Milk
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.71,0:07:09.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And at the edge of the shopping district...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.26,0:07:11.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Hokkaido\NMilk Pudding
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.43,0:07:18.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I smell curry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.69,0:07:27.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I see. Takahashi's family\Nis having curry for dinner tonight.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.20,0:07:30.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I bet he'll be happy about that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.95,0:07:35.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After all, Takahashi loves curry.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.29,0:07:38.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kawamoto, your curry is awesome!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.26,0:07:56.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shikoku, huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.81,0:08:00.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's far from here.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.10,0:08:05.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And Chiho in Iwate is far from here.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.78,0:08:10.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mom, Grandma...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.28,0:08:13.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}and Dad, too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.16,0:08:19.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's always like that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.08,0:08:24.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I take it for granted that tomorrow\Nwill come like it always does...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.17,0:08:29.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and that I'll always be able to see everyone.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.84,0:08:33.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But then I get a surprise.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.43,0:08:40.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just like this, time after time...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.74,0:08:53.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kiriyama, are you sure you don't mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.86,0:08:59.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine. I'll stay here until you get back, Akari.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.66,0:09:03.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, you helped me so much last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.96,0:09:07.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. There's suddenly a party\Nat my aunt's pub.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.75,0:09:10.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Momo's going to stay over at Grandpa's place!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.17,0:09:13.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll come back as soon as I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.68,0:09:14.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.90,0:09:27.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.53,0:09:37.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The entrance exam is the day after tomorrow\Nand I'm like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.58,0:09:42.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be fine. You studied plenty.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.83,0:09:47.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now you just need to rest up\Nand recuperate as much as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.50,0:09:50.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What'll I do if the fever doesn't go down?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.76,0:09:53.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What if...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.72,0:09:57.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I forget everything I've learned?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.76,0:10:01.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You won't forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.93,0:10:03.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.44,0:10:10.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In a little while, you can have some porridge,\Nand then let's take some medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.02,0:10:12.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Until then, get some sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.24,0:10:16.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.45,0:10:21.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's easier to sleep if it's dark,\Nso I'll close the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.91,0:10:23.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.62,0:10:27.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Call me if you need anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.37,0:10:28.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be right next door.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.75,0:10:31.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.19,0:10:58.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And by the morning of the exam,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.28,0:11:02.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}her fever had dropped considerably,\Nto just over 37 degrees.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.83,0:11:06.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hina! Kiriyama has come to pick you up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.41,0:11:08.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What, Rei?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.29,0:11:10.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't have to go to the trouble.\NI'll be okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.25,0:11:13.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's my day off anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.25,0:11:15.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,From school?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.63,0:11:19.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you and the other exam-takers\Nwill be there, so we don't have class today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.72,0:11:21.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.47,0:11:23.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hina, good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.35,0:11:24.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.27,0:11:27.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful of the snow. Don't fail—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.98,0:11:28.98,RightSignM,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,EEK
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.02,0:11:31.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I-I mean, don't trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.23,0:11:34.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Right! See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.41,0:11:43.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}During the time I had the fever,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.45,0:11:49.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I kept thinking about all the people I had lost...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.83,0:11:53.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and the tears wouldn't stop.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.42,0:11:57.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll hold your bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.21,0:12:00.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's okay. I've got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.05,0:12:03.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The sidewalk's iced up,\Nso it could be dangerous. Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.72,0:12:06.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.32,0:12:20.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kiriyama, you're kind of like a mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.15,0:12:22.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.57,0:12:27.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like someone told me that before.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.83,0:12:30.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.38,0:12:46.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But that's right.\NRei suddenly appeared before me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.69,0:13:03.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mom, Grandma, please watch over Hina.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.95,0:13:05.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,CRESCENT MOON
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.87,0:13:17.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck, Hina.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.63,0:13:21.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hina! Are you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.97,0:13:23.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You fell—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.47,0:13:25.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, um, I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.80,0:13:29.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine! I-I just tripped!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.93,0:13:33.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's right.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.10,0:13:36.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Not everyone has gone far away.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.81,0:13:40.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Not everyone has disappeared.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.99,0:13:45.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I mustn't ever forget that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.54,0:13:53.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Passing Time
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.04,0:13:57.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Spring Comes
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.05,0:14:02.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}QUIVER\NQUIVER
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.92,0:14:04.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.88,0:14:09.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}SIZZLE
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.88,0:14:09.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}PIPING HOT
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.14,0:14:11.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Heap of Juicy\NDeep-Fried Chicken
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.14,0:14:12.64,DefaultRightH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eggplant and Meat Gratin\Nwith Plenty of Cheese
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.64,0:14:14.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tuna and Soft Boiled Egg\NMacaroni Salad
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.14,0:14:15.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Garlic Toast
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.64,0:14:17.15,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mini Onigiri\Nand Sweet Pickled Daikon Radish
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.56,0:14:21.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hina, congratulations on passing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.03,0:14:23.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}CELEBRATE
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.78,0:14:26.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's like a mountain of fried meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.90,0:14:26.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}MOUNTAIN
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.99,0:14:31.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's juicy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.20,0:14:32.70,RightSign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,HUFF\NHUFF
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.70,0:14:34.04,EpNum,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Grabbing it\Nwith her\Nhands
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.04,0:14:36.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And the eggplant gratin!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.04,0:14:38.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy!\NLook at all this cheese!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.38,0:14:41.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A huge pile of macaroni salad!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.21,0:14:43.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,With lots of tuna and soft boiled eggs!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.55,0:14:47.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}HUFF\NHUFF
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.88,0:14:47.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?\NI made all your favorites, Hina.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.34,0:14:48.26,RightSignM2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,HOHOHO
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.47,0:14:50.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's really delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.51,0:14:53.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right, everyone, fill up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.14,0:14:55.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For tonight, fried foods are the beverages.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.48,0:14:59.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Since we're celebrating, I got carried away\Nand deep-fried two kilograms of chicken.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.69,0:15:01.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,T-Two kilos?! As beverages?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.19,0:15:03.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Akari, wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.86,0:15:05.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Hina, congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.94,0:15:07.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Thank you, Momo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.45,0:15:11.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I'm moving up too,\Nto senior year of preschool!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.83,0:15:13.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Really, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.87,0:15:18.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My little Hina is becoming\Na high school student.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.12,0:15:20.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Time sure flies.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.00,0:15:23.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm getting old.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.88,0:15:27.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, Akari, knock it off! No mom-speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.80,0:15:29.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're still only 23!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.55,0:15:33.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}But it's really all thanks to Rei.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.39,0:15:37.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Because you helped me with math,\NI was able to solve a lot of mysteries!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.60,0:15:39.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Like proof problems!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.73,0:15:45.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,True, your average math score has gone up\N30 points since Rei started tutoring you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.61,0:15:48.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even though you really didn't like math!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.03,0:15:50.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, that's impressive, kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.61,0:15:53.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I guess professional shogi players\Nare smart cookies.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.70,0:15:57.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much. Can I call you Rei too?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.62,0:15:58.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eat some more.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.83,0:16:00.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Keep eating!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.58,0:16:05.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Uh, th-thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.92,0:16:05.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,HEAP
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.09,0:16:06.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}The Night Before the Exam\N(Flash Back)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.55,0:16:08.72,RightSign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,EHH!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.55,0:16:08.72,LeftSignM2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,RATTLE
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.59,0:16:10.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You left the two of them alone in the house?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.93,0:16:14.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kiriyama is that boy who's always over, right?\NHow old is he now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.60,0:16:16.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A second-year?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.68,0:16:21.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You left a third-year middle schooler and a\Nsecond-year high schooler home alone this late?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.27,0:16:23.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What will you do if something happens?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.73,0:16:25.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If they make a mistake, it'll be too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.94,0:16:27.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You need to go home right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.61,0:16:30.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What'll we do\Nif something happens to Hina?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.74,0:16:35.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, it's all right, Aunt.\NThere's nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.03,0:16:37.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.49,0:16:39.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How can you be so blasé?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.29,0:16:41.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.33,0:16:45.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're talking about Kiriyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.09,0:16:50.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}The Next Day From There\N(Flashback 2)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.09,0:16:50.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}CRESCENT MOON
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.63,0:16:52.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Dad, are you okay with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.72,0:16:55.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how well-behaved he is\Nor that he's helping her study,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.68,0:17:00.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you're letting a young animal\Nhave the run of an all-female house.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.31,0:17:02.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's this, all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.94,0:17:05.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What'll we do if something happens to Hina?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.19,0:17:08.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.69,0:17:12.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,After all, we're talking about the kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.95,0:17:17.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing, nothing's going to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.41,0:17:21.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}Not only Akari, but Dad too!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.58,0:17:24.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}They fully trust a second-year high school boy?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.71,0:17:26.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}Does he really such a safety piece?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.17,0:17:31.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I worry about the future.\NI mean, I have doubts about boys these days.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.63,0:17:37.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Go on, eat. This and this too!\NReally, thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.09,0:17:37.51,RightSignM,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SYMPATHY
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.51,0:17:39.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.60,0:17:46.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Pet me, pet me, pet me right now!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.06,0:17:49.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rei, I'm looking forward to April.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.36,0:17:52.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.16,0:17:59.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Noguchi and the other members\Nof the Shogi Science Club are graduating,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.91,0:18:02.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so I'm happy that you're coming\Nto my school.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.46,0:18:07.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And for some reason,\NMr. Hayashida is thrilled about it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.04,0:18:07.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.08,0:18:10.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's the teacher I met\Nwith the flume noodles, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.46,0:18:11.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That makes me so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.13,0:18:15.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}Yes! Here it comes! Yes!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.13,0:18:16.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}Mr. Hayashida?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.97,0:18:22.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I really don't know how to thank you, Rei.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.68,0:18:27.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even though you had\Na lot of your own work to do,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.06,0:18:29.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,you came here several times a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.94,0:18:33.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. I was studying here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.45,0:18:38.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Besides, I was incredibly careful.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.49,0:18:44.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I got bad results,\Nshe would've thought it was her fault,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.46,0:18:48.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}so I played each and every match\Nas carefully as possible.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.92,0:18:54.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It was a different way of facing things\Nthan I've done up to now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.17,0:19:00.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kid, you have about two more\Nrank-deciding competitions for this period?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.72,0:19:03.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Right now I have eight wins.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.22,0:19:07.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,E-Eight wins in a row?\NSo you’ll go up a class? To B-2?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.06,0:19:11.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Unless something really bad happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.23,0:19:14.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You say it so matter-of-factly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.11,0:19:20.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Hina, he's fine!\NIn that world, the kid is as terrifying as an ogre!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.53,0:19:22.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}Oh man, this guy is scary!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.54,0:19:25.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Ogre? Rei?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.66,0:19:31.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Go up a class?\NThat's a great thing, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.79,0:19:35.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Um, uh, thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.01,0:19:42.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Hina, more juice, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.43,0:19:45.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Juice? What kind?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.47,0:19:50.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}- Cola!\N- You're too young for cola.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.47,0:19:51.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I hate to see her cry\Nor be troubled about something.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.60,0:19:52.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Then orange!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.06,0:19:55.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Okay, hold on. Hup!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.06,0:19:57.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't stand the idea of her being in trouble\Nwith me not knowing about it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.70,0:20:04.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So when I heard she wanted to come to a place\Nthat was within my reach,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.74,0:20:07.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wanted to make sure she was accepted.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.62,0:20:15.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Until then, I thought that whether\Nwhat I did was right or wrong{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.67,0:20:19.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}was something that other people\Nwould decide, as if in a trial.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.26,0:20:24.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But that one day...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.03,0:20:42.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}when she said, "I didn't do anything wrong,"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.53,0:20:45.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and while filled with anxiety,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.03,0:20:51.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}she still kept a firm grip\Non the helm of her heart.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.55,0:21:07.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I found...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.43,0:21:12.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}a light within myself that I didn't have before.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.32,0:21:24.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's right.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.12,0:21:31.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Without a doubt,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.70,0:21:32.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}SHOGI HALL
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.67,0:21:38.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}on that day,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.34,0:21:40.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}she has made...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.13,0:21:44.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}a part of me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.07,0:22:01.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rei.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.32,0:22:09.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.79,0:22:17.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I won today, so I barely managed\Nto avoid a demotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.29,0:22:20.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like I'll be in B-2 next period.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.96,0:22:25.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe we can pick up\Nwhere we left off last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.18,0:22:30.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rei.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.86,0:22:48.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.04,0:23:00.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Spring Comes
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.01,0:24:32.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.01,0:24:37.39,EpNum,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 44
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.43,0:24:34.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Both of you, congratulations\Non your graduation.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.26,0:24:35.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.97,0:24:37.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When are you leaving?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.39,0:24:38.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.93,0:24:41.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hina! Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.19,0:24:43.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to do my best here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.23,0:24:46.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My little sister is too cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.52,0:24:48.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I messed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.23,0:24:50.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm never leaving the house again.
